<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Delete Account Instructions</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd400 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .header p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .warning-box {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .warning-box p {
            color: #856404;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .instructions {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .instruction-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ffd400;
        }

        .instruction-steps {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .step {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .step-number {
            background: #ffd400;
            color: white;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .step-content {
            flex: 1;
            padding-top: 5px;
        }

        .step-content h3 {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .step-content p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .dialog-preview {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .dialog-box {
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid #667eea;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .dialog-header {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .dialog-message {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .dialog-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            justify-content: flex-end;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-cancel {
            background: #e9ecef;
            color: #495057;
        }

        .btn-cancel:hover {
            background: #dee2e6;
        }

        .btn-delete {
            background: #dc3545;
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-delete:hover {
            background: #c82333;
        }

        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 35px;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            background: #ffd400;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #5568d3;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            background: white;
            color: #667eea;
            border: 2px solid #667eea;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .success-message {
            background: #d4edda;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #155724;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            display: none;
        }

        .success-message.show {
            display: block;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 25px;
            }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .action-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>⚠️ Delete Account</h1>
            <p>Instructions to delete your driver account</p>
        </div>

        <!-- <div class="warning-box">
            <p><strong>Warning:</strong> Deleting your account is permanent and cannot be undone. All your data, including driving history, bookings, and earnings will be lost.</p>
        </div> -->

        <div class="instructions">
            <div class="instruction-title">Step-by-Step Instructions</div>
            <div class="instruction-steps">
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Open Your Driver App</h3>
                        <p>Launch the driver application on your device and log in with your credentials.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Go to Profile Page</h3>
                        <p>Navigate to the profile section by tapping the profile icon in the app menu or bottom navigation bar.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Click Delete Account Button</h3>
                        <p>Scroll to the bottom of your profile page and click the "Delete Account" button (usually displayed in red).</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">4</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Review Confirmation Dialog</h3>
                        <p>A confirmation popup will appear asking you to confirm the deletion. Read the warning carefully.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">5</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Confirm Deletion</h3>
                        <p>Click "Yes" in the confirmation dialog to proceed with account deletion.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">6</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Account Deleted</h3>
                        <p>Your account will be deleted. You will be logged out and redirected to the login page.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

